transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I was wondering if you could help me look at my account and make sure that it looks right to you.

Speaker 1: Sure, I can take a look into your account. What's your last name and zip code?

Speaker 2: Last name is Peterson, P-E-T-E-R-S-E-N, zip code 98110.

Speaker 1: Okay, I pulled up your profile here. I see, let's confirm here.

Speaker 2: Okay, so right now it looks like you have a refill date of every three months.

Speaker 1: It's been postponed out, and you have an order that was shipped out on the 6th.

Speaker 2: It looks like it could be a replacement order for your original one.

Speaker 1: Other than that, let me see here, open transit, but it got stuck due to some weather delays,

Speaker 2: so that will be a little bit delayed.

Speaker 1: No worries there.

Speaker 2: Okay, so what alerted my concern, so the original transaction that I did for when I started this account

Speaker 1: was I ordered a 25 prescription of the new Viagra ATV or whatever it is,

Speaker 2: and then while I was doing the purchase, it threw an offer at me for 25 more pills, paid 59 more dollars,

Speaker 1: so I opted for that, but I got 50 pills.

Speaker 2: It turns out they were the wrong ones, so then we did the replacement order last week,

Speaker 1: and then looking at my account, it looks like we only shipped these 40 pills, not 50.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it's going to show up as that, because it's not going to show up as 50,

Speaker 1: but through the system it was sent out as a replacement for the original order.

Speaker 2: So it should be 50 there?

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: And then the other thing that caught my attention is on my account under your prescription,

Speaker 1: there's like a click refill tab, and that now says quantity 40 for $149, where before it said quantity 25.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's just based off the one that they suggested it to for you, to the 40 count,

Speaker 1: because that's what they needed to do on that end.

Speaker 2: However, once that order gets delivered, it will update itself to the 113 for 25.

Speaker 1: Okay, perfect then, so no concerns.

Speaker 2: Yeah, you're all set on that part.

Speaker 1: If any questions come up, let us know, but I hope you have a good day.

Speaker 2: All right, man, thank you.

Speaker 1: I appreciate it.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Take care.

Speaker 1: Bye.
